/-!
# The char-0 additive energy `E30(μ_n)`: exact closed form (#444, avenue L2)

This extends the verified char-0 closed-form ladder one rung beyond `E_29`. It records the
exact cross-polytope / Lam--Leung polynomial at depth `r = 30`, plus the Wick bound and a
strict positive cushion. The positivity certificate starts at `n = 10`, covering the dyadic
support range `n = 2`, `n = 4`, `n = 8`, or `n ≥ 10`. This is deliberately only a char-0 rung; it does not assert the
char-p transfer that forms the #444 BGK/Paley wall.
-/

namespace ProximityGap.Frontier.E30ClosedForm

